name: AstroNut (Fiz1Dy)
description:
A short  shooter platform game consist of 3 levels

  • Tutorial level, Main level, Boss level
  • Mag is scarce till the last level so do aim with precision
  • Aim by using your mouse
  • AD to move either Left & Right
  • W/Spacebar is to Jump
  • E is to enter Door (Edited)
  • Traps 1 shot you
